description:
Dear Colleagues,

Our group has grown enough and it would be very good if we could meetup in person.

I would suggest for the first meeting to start to get to know eachother and also to prepare a plan.

in relation to the psychometric tests it would be useful to discuss:

-your concrete expectations from this group?

-the input and the experience that you can bring in relation to psychometrix tests?

-which parts you would like to develop/improve?

-how you propose to prepare together?

-and any other issue :)

Hopefully all of you will be able to come.

In case some of your friends would also be interested in the topic, feel free to bring them with you.

 

I hope to see you soon,

George
